OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FGranada Reports Correspondent Mel
OL,7,FBarham has been speaking to families
OL,8,Fwho say Bolton Hospice is priceless
OL,10,FJohn Hulme was a private man, but when
OL,11,Fhe got a rare type of cancer called
OL,12,FPMP, his family say Bolton Hospice
OL,13,Fsupported him to die with dignity and
OL,14,Frespect.
OL,16,FNow the hospice needs to fundraise
OL,17,F#5.5 million every year to keep
OL,18,Frunning. They are doing a big push on
OL,19,F2 March as donations will be matched
OL,20,Fby local businesses.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
