PN,39602
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FJohn's step daughter Katy O'Brien
OL,7,Fsaid: "I don't really have words to
OL,8,Fdescribe how important this place is
OL,9,Fto me.
OL,11,F"The hospice needs funding and without
OL,12,Fthat funding places like this will
OL,13,Fclose down, and families and people
OL,14,Fwith illnesses will have nowhere to
OL,15,Fturn."
OL,17,FJohn spent six months being cared for
OL,18,Fby Bolton's hospice at home team,
OL,19,Fbefore he passed away in the hospice
OL,20,Faged just 39.
OL,26,@oD@GOUwD@FO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39603
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FAmy Hulme, John's widow said: "For the
OL,7,Flast 8 days of John's life he came
OL,8,Finto the Hospice. They allowed him the
OL,9,Fprivacy that John wanted, he was a
OL,10,Fvery private person.
OL,12,F"They allowed him to die with dignity,
OL,13,Fand the way that he would have wanted
OL,14,Fto die."
OL,16,FThe support from Bolton Hospice didn't
OL,17,Fstop after John died. They provided
OL,18,Fhis family with grief counselling and
OL,19,Fcreative therapy which they say was
OL,20,Fpriceless.
OL,26,@vD@HO]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
