PN,39604
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FKaty said: "Without the hospice I
OL,7,Fdon't think we would have been able to
OL,8,Fprocess his passing as well as we have.
OL,10,F"It's brought us together as a family
OL,11,Fbecause we know we have our home but
OL,12,Fwe have somewhere we can come if we
OL,13,Fneed that additional support."
OL,15,FThe majority of specialist hospice
OL,16,Fcare is funded not by the government
OL,17,Fbut by donations.
OL,19,FBolton Hospice's running costs are #7
OL,20,Fmillion per year, and #5.5 million of
OL,21,Fthat must come from fundraising.
OL,26,@nD@LOUuD@^O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/10
