PN,39605
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FIt's become harder in recent years as
OL,7,Fthe contributions from the NHS have
OL,8,Fnot kept pace with inflation, and the
OL,9,Frising costs of minimum wage and
OL,10,Fnational insurance contributions the
OL,11,FChief Executive of Bolton Hospice says.
OL,13,FDr Leigh Vallance said: "No matter how
OL,14,Fhard we work, no matter how much
OL,15,Fincome we generate we cannot fill that
OL,16,Fgap on our own.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39606
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,F"The NHS is in such a tight spot right
OL,7,Fnow, it doesn't have the resources.
OL,8,FBut the NHS does understand that
OL,9,Fwithout us they will be in a bigger
OL,10,Fproblem that will cost far more money."
OL,12,FThe hospice was aiming to raise
OL,13,F#100,000 in 36 hours for it's making
OL,14,Fevery moment count campaign - it's
OL,15,Falready hit it's target but still they
OL,16,Fneed to raise more.
OL,18,FBolton Hospice also cared for Harry
OL,19,FLee, who had cancer and pain became
OL,20,Funmanageable at home.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/10
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
