OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,397,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39607
SC,0007
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FHarry's son, Tom Lee said: "We're very
OL,7,Flucky to have the hospice here in
OL,8,FBolton, it's such a relief we were
OL,9,Freally struggling at home prior to him
OL,10,Fbeing admitted into the hospice.
OL,12,F"The deterioration has been so fast
OL,13,Fover the past couple of weeks, that we
OL,14,Fjust weren't managing at home."
OL,16,FHarry died in the hospice after we met
OL,17,Fhis family, and the hospice was there
OL,18,Ffor them.
OL,26,@nD@\OUvD@_O]
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/10
