PN,39608
SC,0008
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F396A1772525050
OL,3,CHospice urgently needs to raise funds
OL,4,Cto keep supporting families
OL,6,FTom said: "It's here for everybody and
OL,7,Fwe need to maintain that. People need
OL,8,Fto make those donations, and they need
OL,9,Fto really get behind it in order for
OL,10,Fit to be here for everybody forever."
OL,12,FThe Hospice campaign is being
OL,13,Fsupported by celebrities like Paddy
OL,14,FMcGuinness and Maxine Peake. The
OL,15,Fcomedian posted encouraging fans to
OL,16,Fdonate on his social media.
OL,18,FHe said: "It will be doubled for
OL,19,Fnothing. What about that? Get
OL,20,Finvolved."
OL,26,@nD@KOUrD@eO]
